column4: Hey guys, I've got a quick question, forgive my confusion here. Which is newer, 11.04 or 10.04 and which is supported? (To me, it seems that 11.04 should be older, but I've been told otherwise)
oh, Ok, so when I was on 10.04, I was told that it needed update to 11.04, but 11.04 isn't supported? Is 11.10 supported?
